{"tid":2051923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有會員開post話食m記都唔得，我就知連登一定會累死香港人革命","createTime":"2020-06-05T06:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T14:30:52.000Z","uid":36788,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"964365829c31af5d6175f92aa5c12c46650ff959","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"香港人革命在於召集全港力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n並唔係篩選最黃既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1994f626b7d9c0ff579fa491b2874e72046ad8fc","tid":2051923,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔又鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d985649545a91b59fb425c35a24eab76e2aee7f2","tid":2051923,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"咁所以你咁睇重一個半個會員嘅説話做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538ec5867f9be572b74bf48871c0cdf6022032b3","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"食藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食紅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf8a361643eec30555540a94769f8945a1bd436","tid":2051923,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"邊個post?"},{"pid":"9a3f512bb6b960cd7d8778906f2a25ca0777628c","tid":2051923,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"我屋企附近有黃店我一定食黃店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031072ec9fef438f6b227eb97c343696f2ed5125","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"538ec5867f9be572b74bf48871c0cdf6022032b3","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"食藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食紅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬥紅係同黃絲鬥<br />\n一齊食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8b1e065b4860801511ae5a5d9eca95b623c9e0","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"黃店一定係首選，但如果冇幫襯非藍店中資係冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7a4ec000cf375565b52a105338da139a438085","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"2021年 黃絲人數：700萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n只要屈個藍絲係黃 <br />\n我地就可以光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bd105f0de071a9fe378fac81e1d59c93de2989","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031072ec9fef438f6b227eb97c343696f2ed5125","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"538ec5867f9be572b74bf48871c0cdf6022032b3","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"食藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食紅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬥紅係同黃絲鬥<br />\n一齊食m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"M記個M字好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj