id":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bb90ebe2918ffe0a82e27241d107bbf8b1984a4","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6b8d5c2fe191bba94ab7c949228af2eec32896","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"食m記 = 展現民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kNBUHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kNBUHh.jpg&h=9833c2e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"食M記睇tvb玩ps係連登仔嘅民主自由<br />\n死五毛收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"除左五毛熱狗分化撚之外<br />\n全世界都係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20f58fb30ea3af2458b0a9dc2b1b7c3e1085ae2","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e8c226a796c49eed2e84a342a762200e45c1f78","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6b8d5c2fe191bba94ab7c949228af2eec32896","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"食m記 = 展現民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kNBUHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kNBUHh.jpg&h=9833c2e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪想支持黃既人愈黎愈少？人數永遠係抗爭既首要<br />\n<br />\n唔係check你有幾黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"2021年 黃絲人數：700萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屈個藍絲係黃 我地就可以光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f49860f8b16fa98aa3c9685ea7b53b934c1a78c","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>2019年6月開始：</strong><br />\n全民反對逃犯條例，港豬喚醒，黃絲人數大增。發動香港史上最大型遊行。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：&gt;200萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019年11月：</strong><br />\n區選大勝，民意創新高，黃絲士氣大增。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：&gt;200萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年1月：</strong><br />\n黃色經濟圈初成。但會員「月野兔兔」開始批鬥文化，影藍店食客大頭，連黨報環球時報都撰文批評。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zR7KkTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzR7KkTH.jpg&h=6d2928b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幸好連登仔心水清，及時撥亂反正。原來我地追求民主、自由，就係食藍店嘅自由。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJ9wZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJ9wZ8.jpg&h=45972c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食藍店=展現民主自由=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：250萬，開始持續上升</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年2月：</strong><br />\n男人eeetv成員李萬璣慘被批鬥，被指控為藍絲，黃衛兵翻舊帳，指出李萬璣曾撐警。其後李萬璣及時澄清，表示自己屬於「黃&hellip;&hellip;掛？」。<br />\n<br />\n爭論一翻後，黃絲接納其解釋，並將李萬璣等「黃&hellip;&hellip;掛？」人士，列為自己人、同路人，以免有人心灰意冷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0i76zk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0i76zk0.jpg&h=6df0275b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「 黃&hellip;&hellip;掛？」=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：280萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年4月：</strong><br />\nMr Wally欠機票錢，於facebook專頁發起眾籌，引黎大批連衛兵批鬥。有連衛兵表示Wally撐警。經查證後，Mr Wally曾經講過「香港人加油」，facebook更post過🖐🏻☝🏻，暗示五大訴求，缺一不可，因此明顯係手足。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hotNOG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hotNOG.jpg&h=81aafa10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TNxKk8Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTNxKk8Q.jpg&h=de3f6af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撐警，但講「香港人加油」=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：400萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年5月：</strong><br />\n政府推出抗疫基金，大量黃色小店爭相到銀行開戶口，領取補貼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然匯豐銀行會見港澳辦後，凍結星火帳戶。但由於有高層老公係前線手足，高層個老公黃=公司黃，所以黃店開戶，首選匯豐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6a6WcdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6a6WcdY.jpg&h=0e686474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORLPxd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORLPxd9.jpg&h=18010f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高層老公黃=黃，匯豐客戶就當然係黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：450萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年6月：</strong><br />\n全球疫情消退，黃絲準備買機票去旅行。<br />\n有黃絲提醒我地，國泰、港龍係香港人嘅公司，老共想搞佢好耐。所以即使之前炒晒手足，鼓勵篤灰清算，大家都決定繼續幫襯國泰，支持黃色航空公司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm67iWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm67iWC.jpg&h=c38cb9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總部喺香港=香港人公司=黃，搭國泰嘅都係手足<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：480萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年7月：</strong><br />\n取得共識，決定進一步擴大黃色經濟圈準則。<br />\n中立=黃<br />\n唔表態=黃<br />\n仲諗緊=黃<br />\n藍店扮黃=黃<br />\n黃店但唔捐錢唔貼文宣唔聘請手足=黃<br />\n<br />\n同時，黃納粹被逐出連登。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YTUJti.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YTUJti.jpg&h=29330dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：580萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 2020年8月：</strong><br />\n重返街頭抗爭，民陣舉辦大遊行打響頭炮。<br />\n遊行隊伍由3點行到10點，警方數字25萬人，民陣表示，遊行人士接近600萬人，當中包括200萬人現場參與，另加400萬黃絲以各種方式參與，包括：在家觀看直播、光顧黃店、精神上支持等等。<br />\n<br />\n去/唔去遊行=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：600萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 2020年9月：</strong><br />\n立法會選舉展開，由於黃色光譜甚為廣闊，除少部分黃納粹外，所有候選人勻屬黃絲。選舉結果一如所料，黃絲議員大勝。<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨有個皇字=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：650萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 2020年10月：</strong><br />\n黃納粹退出連登後，黃絲數目與日俱增。由於門檻降低，大部分香港人自動成為黃絲。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你係黃=黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數： 670萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 2020年12月：</strong><br />\nUST南亞仔便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「撐警不能算藍&hellip;&hellip;黃的標準比天高！&hellip;&hellip;支持政府的事，能算藍麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「黃納粹」，什麼「連衛兵」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：680萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong> 2021年1月：</strong><br />\n香港黃絲人數尚欠20萬，大家一致決定將標準降至無下限，最緊要包容、接納，唔再犯黃納粹嘅錯誤。最終令所有人成為黃絲，壯大黃圈。<br />\n<br />\n篤尿黃=黃<br />\n底褲黃=黃<br />\n高層藍前線黃=黃<br />\n老豆藍個仔黃=黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6ZHSEC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6ZHSEC.jpg&h=0edab97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲人數：700萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>連登仔：700萬黃絲，即係光復左香港</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3de9c9bef807aff50abc50bc30c9debedb0b8b00","tid":2051923,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cf8a361643eec30555540a94769f8945a1bd436","tid":2051923,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"邊個post?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2051888/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2051888/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"d2b2f916cb9c3164e04986a4ce94401921f608d8","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a20f58fb30ea3af2458b0a9dc2b1b7c3e1085ae2","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e8c226a796c49eed2e84a342a762200e45c1f78","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6b8d5c2fe191bba94ab7c949228af2eec32896","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"食m記 = 展現民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kNBUHh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kNBUHh.jpg&h=9833c2e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪想支持黃既人愈黎愈少？人數永遠係抗爭既首要<br />\n<br />\n唔係check你有幾黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"2021年 黃絲人數：700萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屈個藍絲係黃 我地就可以光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"十四億黃絲指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2b62fbc6b2223ad20e787a69793b850fff9c5e","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2b2f916cb9c3164e04986a4ce94401921f608d8","tid":2051923,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a20f58fb30ea3af2458b0a9dc2b1b7c3e1085ae2","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e8c226a796c49eed2e84a342a762200e45c1f78","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"你係咪想支持黃既人愈黎愈少？人數永遠係抗爭既首要<br />\n<br />\n唔係check你有幾黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"2021年 黃絲人數：700萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1967779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1967779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屈個藍絲係黃 我地就可以光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"十四億黃絲指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"共產黨話驚到瀨屎<br />\n不過共產黨都可以係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2e4f57dc0ad798fa40a5b9b06f60c7cb052ef0","tid":2051923,"uid":159631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"係有班5毛起到鬥黃 搞分化"},{"pid":"52d7fd08b433cb525a1259e4843140ddd5595c71","tid":2051923,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2e4f57dc0ad798fa40a5b9b06f60c7cb052ef0","tid":2051923,"uid":159631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"係有班5毛起到鬥黃 搞分化"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"你以為，大部分都係連登仔自己鬥"},{"pid":"18da05f8a1b9aca39d347cf23db48d8f3f88dd19","tid":2051923,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1994f626b7d9c0ff579fa491b2874e72046ad8fc","tid":2051923,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔又鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"不鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkOxs4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkOxs4J.jpg&h=b0da2df5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}